---
title: Mediterranean Tomato & Oregano Gnocchi with Capers & Feta
description: Bring a taste of the Mediterranean to your table tonight with oregano, sun-dried tomato pesto and feta coming together in a rich sauce that’s a perfect match for the crispy edges and pillowy centres of pan-fried gnocchi.
